# Principles
	+ ASAP

# Characteristics
	+ Reproducibility
	+ Reuseablity
	+ Tracability
	
# Structure
What does the researcher want ?
Reserachers conduct control experiments to create useful model.
Model -> LearningProcedure(Data, ModelArchitecture)

# Conditions of experiment
	+ Data -> Dataloader ->  Dataset + Batching + Transform
	+ ModelArchitecture 
	+ LearningProcedure -> Evaluator + Update + Log + ModelArchitecture + Data
		+ Evaluator ->  LossFunction + Metrics 
		+ Update -> Optimizer, LearningRateScheduler
		+ Log -> Proceduredumb 

# How researchers set up a control experiment ?
+ Change any experiment conditions optionally
+ Run experiment 
